.TH AUDITAS 1 "January 2026" "1.0.0" "Auditas Audio Integrity Suite"
.SH NAME
auditas \- Verify and maintain your digital music collection
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B auditas
.I COMMAND
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.RI [ ARGUMENTS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B auditas
is a professional-grade toolkit for verifying, repairing, and managing large digital music collections. It supports FLAC, MP3, and other formats, with a focus on data integrity and batch processing.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.BR verify " (alias: " v )
Verify integrity of FLAC files using parallel processing.
.TP
.B md5
Scan for or fix missing FLAC MD5 checksums.
.TP
.B batch
Run a comprehensive workflow (Verify -> MD5 -> ReplayGain -> Audit).
.TP
.B replaygain
Apply ReplayGain (R128) tags to FLAC albums.
.TP
.B audit
Audit FLAC encoder versions and first-track integrity.
.TP
.B tag-audit
Audit files for missing tags and cover art quality.
.TP
.B mp3
Scan or fix MP3 library integrity and VBR headers.
.TP
.B verify-gen
Verify OGG, Opus, M4A, WAV, and AIFF files.
.TP
.B reencode
Re-encode FLACs in the current folder (with verification).
.TP
.B clean
Remove temporary backup files and directories.
.TP
.B check-deps
Check for required external tools.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message for the tool or a specific command.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show version information.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/auditas/config
User configuration file.
.TP
.I ~/.local/state/auditas/logs/
Directory containing execution logs.
